dct_title_s: The Rand McNally new commercial atlas map of New York.
dct_description_sm: Rand McNally & Co. Inset : southeast area map continued. Map shows railroads and steamship lines. Principal cities are listed and located. List of New York railroads. Verso: New York counties, creeks, islands, lakes and ponds, mountains, rivers, and towns. New York electric lines.
